msgid "Welcome to Duka Mwecheche!"
msgstr "Karibu Duka Mwecheche!"

msgid "This quick tutorial will guide you through the key features of your dashboard. You can always replay it from the menu under your username."
msgstr "Mwongozo huu mfupi utakuelekeza kwenye vipengele muhimu vya dashibodi yako. Unaweza kuucheza tena wakati wowote kutoka kwenye menyu iliyo chini ya jina lako la mtumiaji."

msgid "Your Dashboard"
msgstr "Dashibodi Yako"

msgid "Your <strong>Supplier Dashboard</strong> shows key stats: active clients, pending bids, won bids, and open procurement requests."
msgstr "<strong>Dashibodi ya Msambazaji</strong> yako inaonyesha takwimu muhimu: wateja hai, zabuni zinazosubiri, zabuni zilizoshinda, na maombi ya ununuzi yaliyo wazi."

msgid "Click <strong>Browse Requests</strong> to find procurement opportunities from businesses. Submit competitive bids to win supply contracts."
msgstr "Bofya <strong>Tazama Maombi</strong> kupata fursa za ununuzi kutoka kwa biashara. Wasilisha zabuni shindani ili ushinde mikataba ya usambazaji."

msgid "Track Your Bids"
msgstr "Fuatilia Zabuni Zako"

msgid "Under <strong>My Bids</strong>, monitor the status of all your bid submissions — pending, awarded, or rejected."
msgstr "Chini ya <strong>Zabuni Zangu</strong>, fuatilia hali ya zabuni zako zote zilizowasilishwa — zinasubiri, zimepewa, au zimekataliwa."

msgid "Connect with Businesses"
msgstr "Ungana na Biashara"

msgid "Use <strong>Browse Businesses</strong> to discover potential clients. Apply to become their approved supplier."
msgstr "Tumia <strong>Tazama Biashara</strong> kugundua wateja watarajiwa. Omba kuwa msambazaji wao aliyeidhinishwa."

msgid "Client Relationships"
msgstr "Mahusiano ya Wateja"

msgid "Once approved, view your client list under <strong>My Clients</strong>. Build strong relationships for repeat procurement."
msgstr "Ukishaidhinishwa, tazama orodha ya wateja wako chini ya <strong>Wateja Wangu</strong>. Jenga mahusiano imara kwa ununuzi wa kurudiwa."

msgid "You're All Set!"
msgstr "Uko Tayari!"

msgid "Start browsing procurement requests to grow your supply network! Replay this tutorial from your username menu anytime."
msgstr "Anza kutazama maombi ya ununuzi ili kukuza mtandao wako wa usambazaji! Cheza mwongozo huu tena kutoka kwenye menyu ya jina lako la mtumiaji wakati wowote."

msgid "Your <strong>Rider Dashboard</strong> shows active deliveries, completed orders, and your performance score."
msgstr "<strong>Dashibodi ya Mpanda Baiskeli</strong> yako inaonyesha usafirishaji unaoendelea, oda zilizokamilika, na alama yako ya utendaji."

msgid "Availability Toggle"
msgstr "Badili Upatikanaji"

msgid "Toggle your <strong>availability</strong> status so businesses know when you are ready to accept deliveries."
msgstr "Badili hali yako ya <strong>upatikanaji</strong> ili biashara zijue wakati uko tayari kupokea usafirishaji."

msgid "View your current delivery assignments under <strong>Active Deliveries</strong>. See customer details, location, and order amounts."
msgstr "Tazama kazi zako za sasa za usafirishaji chini ya <strong>Usafirishaji Unaoendelea</strong>. Ona maelezo ya mteja, eneo, na kiasi cha oda."

msgid "Check <strong>Delivery History</strong> for a complete record of all your past deliveries."
msgstr "Angalia <strong>Historia ya Usafirishaji</strong> kwa rekodi kamili ya usafirishaji wako wote wa zamani."

msgid "Track your total earnings and delivery count under <strong>My Earnings</strong>."
msgstr "Fuatilia mapato yako yote na idadi ya usafirishaji chini ya <strong>Mapato Yangu</strong>."

msgid "Stay available to receive delivery assignments! Replay this tutorial from your username menu anytime."
msgstr "Endelea kupatikana ili upokee kazi za usafirishaji! Cheza mwongozo huu tena kutoka kwenye menyu ya jina lako la mtumiaji wakati wowote."

